{"tid":2088090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維穩亂洗錢議案又獲通過，泛民你班垃圾反正係立法會都投白票架啦，9月仲選你地入去把撚呀","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:22:11.000Z","uid":60916,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d304aabb505b9195debd3606204412994be8fc1","tid":2088090,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"財委會通過撥款200億元予社署 購160個物業作社福用途<br />\n2020-06-30 16:55<br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會通過撥款200億元予社會福利署，在全港各區購買約160個物業，以提供福利設施。跨黨派議員關注當局沒有優先考慮採用政府閒置土地及處所，又指預算過高、無善用空置校舍。有議員擔心批出一筆過撥款後，日後無法監察。社署則承諾，每年將到立法會匯報購買物業的進展，亦會貼近市價購入物業，不會造成托市。//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>缺席泛民議員包括：梁耀忠、涂謹申、李國麟、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Few3h5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFew3h5O.png&h=35f53df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪撚搬去政事台<br />\n你搬一個我開一個"},{"pid":"0cf15f688b180be956fc09c63850df43fb3da946","tid":2088090,"uid":63822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 周俊樂(-10)</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</